### Send a payment request
POST http://localhost:8080/api/payments
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "amount": 200.50,
  "currency": "USD",
  "description": "Payment for services"
}

### Send a payment request with ID
POST http://localhost:8080/api/payments
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "id": "custom-payment-id-123",
  "amount": 200.75,
  "currency": "EUR",
  "description": "Payment with custom ID"
}